cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with point cloud data and tasks such as object detection, segmentation, and shape completion. It also involves tracking, 3D reconstruction, and pose estimation, which are common topics in the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. The use of deep learning and neural networks suggests that it could also be classified under the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper involves geometric algorithms and computational geometry, which are relevant to the Graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
